  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield quotes an obituary: \"Ethan, a triplet, was born first at 4:43 pm on a beautiful Tuesday evening in October.  He was born at Swedish Hospital in Seattle. Maizie arrived shortly after at 4:44 and Hunter at 4:45. Our family spent the first year and half living in Olympia at Summit Lake and then we moved to Conway.\" [https://www.hawthornefh.com/obituary/ethan-chapin].\\n\\nVarious websites (including Find a Grave) incorrectly give his birth date as 28 October 2002, which was a Monday. His mother has posted birthday wishes to her triplets on her Instagram on 29 October of several years, and as reported in an NBC news article, \"In an Oct. 29 Instagram post, [his girlfriend, Xana] Kernodle wished him a happy birthday and said life was \"so much better with you in it.\"\" [https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/mother-victim-idaho-university-slayings-says-family-wont-attend-suspec-rcna87469].\\n",
